msgid "# Flash Attention 3"
msgstr "# Flash Attention 3"

msgid ""
"Flash Attention 3 on Ascend is currently in beta. The `flash_attn_npu` package required for FA3 has been open-sourced on GitHub.\n"
"    Please refer to the [flash-attention-npu repository](https://github.com/MinghuasLab/flash-attention-npu) for more details."
msgstr ""
"Ascend 上的 Flash Attention 3 目前处于测试阶段。FA3 所需的 `flash_attn_npu` 包已在 GitHub 上开源。\n"
"    更多详情请参考 [flash-attention-npu 仓库](https://github.com/MinghuasLab/flash-attention-npu)。"

msgid "## Motivation"
msgstr "## 动机"

msgid ""
"- **Training-inference consistency**: Ensures that the attention computation during inference matches the training side, which is essential for RL workflows (e.g., veRL) where inference results are used to compute training signals.\n"
"- **Framework debugging**: Consistent attention implementations make it easier to debug issues by eliminating discrepancies between training and inference.\n"
"- **Reinforcement Learning (RL)**: RL training often requires deterministic and consistent rollouts for reproducibility and stable training."
msgstr ""
"- **训练-推理一致性**：确保推理时的注意力计算与训练侧一致，这对于强化学习工作流（例如 veRL）至关重要，因为推理结果用于计算训练信号。\n"
"- **框架调试**：一致的注意力实现消除了训练和推理之间的差异，使问题调试更加容易。\n"
"- **强化学习 (RL)**：RL 训练通常需要确定性和一致的推演，以实现可重复性和稳定训练。"

msgid "## Feature Comparison"
msgstr "## 特性对比"

msgid "### Differences from GPU Implementation"
msgstr "### 与 GPU 实现的差异"

msgid ""
"1. **Unsupported features on NPU FA3**: Sliding window attention, RoPE, ALiBi, Softcapping, and FP8 quantization are not yet supported.\n"
"2. **Graph capture**: The tiling of `flash_attn_with_kvcache` is processed on the host side and is currently being optimized. It does not support ACL graph capture (i.e., cannot be captured into a computational graph for acceleration). Please use `compilation_config={\"cudagraph_mode\": \"PIECEWISE\"}` when enabling FA3."
msgstr ""
"1. **NPU FA3 不支持的特性**：尚不支持滑动窗口注意力、RoPE、ALiBi、Softcapping 和 FP8 量化。\n"
"2. **图捕获**：`flash_attn_with_kvcache` 的 tile 划分在主机端处理，目前正在优化中。它不支持 ACL 图捕获（即无法捕获到计算图中进行加速）。启用 FA3 时，请使用 `compilation_config={\"cudagraph_mode\": \"PIECEWISE\"}`。"

msgid "## Hardware Requirements"
msgstr "## 硬件要求"

msgid ""
"FA3 currently requires Ascend Atlas A2 and A3 inference products NPUs.\n"
"We will support other NPUs in the future."
msgstr ""
"FA3 目前需要 Ascend Atlas A2 和 A3 推理产品 NPU。\n"
"未来我们将支持其他 NPU。"

msgid "## Software Requirements"
msgstr "## 软件要求"

msgid "### Installation"
msgstr "### 安装"

msgid "## Enabling Flash Attention 3"
msgstr "## 启用 Flash Attention 3"

msgid ""
"1. Set the environment variable `export VLLM_BATCH_INVARIANT=1` to enable batch invariant mode\n"
"2. Specify the attention backend as `FLASH_ATTN` via the LLM parameter `attention_backend=\"FLASH_ATTN\"`"
msgstr ""
"1. 设置环境变量 `export VLLM_BATCH_INVARIANT=1` 以启用批次不变模式\n"
"2. 通过 LLM 参数 `attention_backend=\"FLASH_ATTN\"` 将注意力后端指定为 `FLASH_ATTN`"

msgid "### Online Inference (Server Mode)"
msgstr "### 在线推理（服务器模式）"

msgid "### Offline Inference"
msgstr "### 离线推理"

msgid "## Limitations"
msgstr "## 限制"

msgid ""
"- **Package not yet open-sourced**: The `flash_attn_npu` package required for FA3 has not yet been released. External users cannot use FA3 until the package is available.\n"
"- **Sliding window not supported**: FA3 does not support sliding window attention. Models that require sliding window need to use the default FIA backend.\n"
"- **ACL graph capture not supported**: The tiling of `flash_attn_with_kvcache` is processed on the host side and currently does not support ACL graph capture. Please use `compilation_config={\"cudagraph_mode\": \"PIECEWISE\"}` when enabling FA3.\n"
"- **RoPE not supported**: FA3 does not support rotary position embedding within the attention kernel. vLLM-Ascend patches this by using the PyTorch native RoPE fallback instead.\n"
"- **ALiBi not supported**: FA3 does not support ALiBi (Attention with Linear Biases).\n"
"- **Softcapping not supported**: FA3 does not support attention logit softcapping.\n"
"- **FP8 quantization not supported**: FA3 does not support FP8 quantized attention.\n"
"- **MLA and SFA not supported**: FA3 does not support Multi-head Latent Attention (MLA) or Sparse Flash Attention (SFA)."
msgstr ""
"- **包尚未开源**：FA3 所需的 `flash_attn_npu` 包尚未发布。在包可用之前，外部用户无法使用 FA3。\n"
"- **不支持滑动窗口**：FA3 不支持滑动窗口注意力。需要滑动窗口的模型需要使用默认的 FIA 后端。\n"
"- **不支持 ACL 图捕获**：`flash_attn_with_kvcache` 的 tile 划分在主机端处理，目前不支持 ACL 图捕获。启用 FA3 时，请使用 `compilation_config={\"cudagraph_mode\": \"PIECEWISE\"}`。\n"
"- **不支持 RoPE**：FA3 不支持注意力内核中的旋转位置编码。vLLM-Ascend 通过使用 PyTorch 原生 RoPE 回退来修补此问题。\n"
"- **不支持 ALiBi**：FA3 不支持 ALiBi（线性偏置注意力）。\n"
"- **不支持 Softcapping**：FA3 不支持注意力 logit softcapping。\n"
"- **不支持 FP8 量化**：FA3 不支持 FP8 量化注意力。\n"
"- **不支持 MLA 和 SFA**：FA3 不支持多头潜在注意力 (MLA) 或稀疏闪存注意力 (SFA)。"

msgid "## Tested Models"
msgstr "## 已测试模型"

msgid ""
"- **Qwen3 (Dense)**: `Qwen/Qwen3-0.6B`, `Qwen/Qwen3-1.7B`, `Qwen/Qwen3-8B`\n"
"- **Qwen3 (MoE)**: `Qwen/Qwen3-30B-A3B`"
msgstr ""
"- **Qwen3 (密集模型)**：`Qwen/Qwen3-0.6B`、`Qwen/Qwen3-1.7B`、`Qwen/Qwen3-8B`\n"
"- **Qwen3 (MoE)**：`Qwen/Qwen3-30B-A3B`"

